reviewText: My husband is very happy with this.
Interesting look at the Australian SF series but all Reality.

From the DVD case ~
OVER SIX HOURS OF EXCITING BONUS FEATURES:
Farscape Undressed: the Home Video Premiere of the Rarely Seen, Long Sought-After Behind-the-Scenes Special.
Listening In with Composer Guy Gross Featurettes for 12 Episodes.
Behind-the -Scenes Interviews with the Characters, Cast, and Creative Team of Farscape.
Including 'Zhaan Forever' with Virginia Hey.
Color/2 discs
Approx. 6 hrs., 7 mins. total

These 2 discs contain the exact same content as the 3 disc set of The Archives included in the 15th Anniversary Edition of Farscape the Complete Series, out on Flatiron Film, less 27 mins. of content comprised of the 2 extras Psychotically Ambitious and Memories of Moya.  If you have the Complete Series this set is redundant.  If you haven't seen these extras and you are a big enough Farscape fan to have read this far then I highly recommend them to you.  Prepare for Starburst people!
Love Farscape watch it many times its a different space show not like the rest my husband calles it the blue people show but he watches too
Would absolutely love to know what the heck is on the DVD other than special edition! I hate it when sellers just put up something, say special and think HEY THEY WILL BUY IT NOT KNOWING ANYTHING!
